column5: I would like to bring my nephews to go Victoria Harbour for some pan fish fishing. can any member tell me where I can get some crappie in this area?  please email me at    [emailÂ protected]  Thanks in advance!
I don't know about Georgian Bay in particular, but we never seem to get any crappie around here in the Kawarthas in the fall.  Lots around come April/May though.
